programme.desc: The second edition of the FIFA Arab Cup is scheduled to be held in Qatar from December 1 to 18, 2025. The tournament will be hosted across six venues, all of which were utilized during the FIFA World Cup™ three years prior. Stay updated with comprehensive coverage of the Arab Cup Qatar 2025 on BeIN Sports News.
